name: STATE v. Fritz CROMWELL, et al.

parties: STATE v. Fritz CROMWELL, et al.

opinions.text:
ORDER
Pursuant to the parties’ motion, and in light of this courts decision in D & J Enterprises, Inc. et al. v. Michaelson, Attorney General et al., 121 R.I. 537, 401 A.2d 440 (1979), this case is hereby remanded to the Superior Court for further proceedings.

attorneys: Dennis J. Roberts II, Atty. Gen., for plaintiff.
Leonard A. Kamaras, John F. Sheehan, Providence, for defendant.
casebody.head_matter:
STATE v. Fritz CROMWELL, et al.
No. 83-8-C.A.
Supreme Court of Rhode Island.
March 3, 1983.
Dennis J. Roberts II, Atty. Gen., for plaintiff.
Leonard A. Kamaras, John F. Sheehan, Providence, for defendant.
